snippet.title: System shock- Intro
snippet.description:
This is the intro to the classic PC game, system shock.
You can download System Shock Portable by following this link. Basically, it's the original game modified to run on modern operating systems. If you have any problems in getting it to run, feel free to PM me.
http://www.strangebedfellows.de/index.php/topic,211.0.html
